User access-t gondoljuk ujra:
- van a user -> van az auth lepes (authentication) -> (authentication nem authorization) -> nyilik a sessoin -> features access -> data access
- User Provider: 
	- reload from session - minden req vegen serializalva bemegy a user obj. a sessionbe, innen epiti ujra
		- man in the middel tamadasoknak lehet kiteve
	- load the user - reach for user data (db, API) 
	- Custom User Provider - for example from API
	- Authentication Providers - its like a middleware, runs before the controller
	- Guard authenticator - dont use the built in one
		- class xyAuthenticator extends AbstractGuardAuthenticator
		- security.yml -ban konfigolhato
